      <title>Endeavour 同意向员工支付加班费以结束罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/endeavour-agrees-to-pay-staff-for-overtime-work-to-end-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Endeavour Mining Plc 同意向其位于塞内加尔的 Sabodala 矿场的员工支付加班费，以结束为期五天的罢工，直至找到更持久的解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/endeavour-agrees-to-pay-staff-for-overtime-work-to-end-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
